en-US.description:
That concert you wanted to see? It was last week. Don’t miss out again. Capture every event you see with a screenshot. Save them all in one list. Share with friends—no app needed.

Soonlist summarizes your screenshots into one clean list like a friend who always knows what’s happening. No typing. No copy/paste. Just possibilities.

One tap adds it to your calendar. Share a single event or your whole list. Friends don't need the app to see what you share.

Key Features:
• Save every event you see
• Capture events in seconds
• See all your possibilities in one place
• Share links with friends
• Add to calendar in one tap

Turn "I meant to go" into "glad I went."

For more information, please review our Terms of Service (https://www.soonlist.com/terms-ios) and Privacy Policy (https://www.soonlist.com/privacy).
en-US.releaseNotes: Improved notifications help you keep track of events you captured
en-US.title: Soonlist Save Events Instantly
